[0m[49m[39m  462, 462[0m:[39m[49m   "query_time_ms": 23
[0m[49m[39m  463, 463[0m:[39m[49m }
[0m[49m[39m  464, 464[0m:[39m[49m ```
[0m[49m[39m  465, 465[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  466, 466[0m:[39m[49m **Sample output for a "crosswalks" query:**
[0m[49m[39m  467, 467[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  468, 468[0m:[39m[49m ```json
